    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FEATURES:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Procedurally Generated Levels</strong>: Every run is different – experience fresh, thrilling missions with unpredictable challenges.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unstoppable Zombie Hordes</strong>: Fight through waves of zombies, mastering your weapons and strategically using your character abilities.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Multiple Characters with Unique Abilities</strong>: Choose from a variety of characters, each with their own powerful abilities that can make the difference between life and death.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dynamic Weapon Variety</strong>: From shotguns and rifles to explosive weapons – develop diverse strategies to take on the hordes.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Constant Progression</strong>: Level up during each mission, improve your gear, and upgrade your passive abilities to better prepare for escalating threats.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Adrenaline-Pumping Gameplay</strong>: With fast reflexes and strategic thinking, survive even the most dangerous situations.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every round in <strong>Endless Deaths</strong> is an exciting adventure where you’ll face new challenges repeatedly. The rogue-like mechanics ensure that no two runs are the same, offering fresh opportunities to improve your survival skills with each playthrough.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Are You Ready to Escape the Zombie Horde?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can you survive the endless onslaught and make it to the safe house, or will you become just another victim of <strong>Endless Deaths</strong>? Every mistake could be your last, but every victory brings you one step closer to your goal.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Endless Deaths</strong> offers endless replayability, thrilling combat, and constant progression that will keep you returning for more. Step into the apocalypse – if you dare!</p>",
